title: Amazon Basics Dog and Cat Feeder Dispenser for Food and Water, Small, Pack of 2, Grey
features: 2-in-1 bundle: small pet waterer with 1-gallon capacity and small pet feeder with 6-pound capacity; uses gravity to ensure a consistent supply of food and water
Waterer base made of PP and bottle made of PET; feeder’s lid and base made of PP and hopper made of PET
Side cut-out handles along base for easy lifting; non-skid rubber feet for secure placement; ideal for cats or dogs in single- or multiple-pet homes
Extra-wide-mouth food hopper and water bottle for easy filling and cleaning; hand wash only
Pet feeder measures 12.5 by 7 by 12 inches (LxWxH); pet waterer measures 12.4 by 7 by 12 inches (LxWxH)
description: From the manufacturer Gravity Pet Feeder and Waterer Keep pets happily fed and watered with our gravity pet feeders and waterers. As supply low, the storage hopper automatically releases more. Easy to Use Simply unscrew the lid and fill the hopper with up to 2,7 kg of dry pet food (feeder) or water (waterer). Each design allows level dispensing. Durable Design These convenient pet pals feature a PP lid and base with a transparent storage hopper, which makes it easy to check food or water levels at a glance. Side Handles and Non-Slip Feet Convenient side cut-outs along the base serve as integrated side handles for easy lifting. Non-skid rubber feet help ensure secure placement.
